Bards at lvl 58 or so, completely LOSE their primary group role because they cannot mez mobs if they do LDoNs with higher level players.  The lvl 60 Mez is so rare, you really can't count that.  So, until lvl 62, you can't mez crap.  Heck, until you get lvl 61, you sometimes can't even LULL mobs on LDoN missions.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
