				<td colspan="2"><span>&quot;Hold Aggro&quot; is different from &quot;Grab Aggro&quot;.
<br />

<br />
Some bards would like to really tank, others would like to be able to snap grab aggro like rangers do with taunt/snare or warriors do with taunt. (Taunt doesn't hold aggro, it grabs it until it is either held by the warrior or snatched away).
<br />

<br />
I am greedy and would like both, but for my play style, a temporary snap grab is adequate.</span></td>
